November 16, 2000 65 FR 69331 Abandoned Mine Land Reclamation Program Guidelines ACTION: Notice of intent.
The Office of Surface Mining Reclamation and Enforcement (OSM) proposes to amend the Abandoned Mine Land (AML) Reclamation Program Guidelines published on December 30, 1996 (61 FR 68777).
The proposed changes will make the guidelines easier to read and understand.
The changes also incorporate new procedures found in the AML Enhancement Rule published February 12, 1999 (64 FR 7482).
Comments are requested.
